    {
      "para_id": "Q001983.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) Enlil-bani , the shepherd , who makes everything abundant for Nibru , the farmer of Urim’s plentiful barley , who purifies all divine powers of Eridug , the favourite en - priest of Unug , king of Isin , king of Sumer and Akkad , the spouse chosen in the heart by Inana ."
    }
  ],
